videos.description: QB Tanner Mangum completes a 23-yard pass to Micah Simon and he makes a leaping grab for the touchdown.
videos.headline: BYU strikes on first possession

videos.description: Tanner Mangum finds his TE Matt Bushman for the 11-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Cougars offense looks sharp on TD

videos.description: Mangum attempts a pass to his receiver but it is tipped and Dakari Monroe catches the interception with one hand for the turnover.
videos.headline: San Jose State CB Monroe makes a crazy pick

videos.description: Spartan QB Montel Aaron has a miscommunication with his receiver and throws the interception to Michael Shelton.
videos.headline: BYU  dominant so far on defense

videos.description: Tanner Mangum throws it up to Aleva Hifo and he makes a terrific catch with a defender all over him for 42 yards.
videos.headline: Cougars WR Hifo makes a tough catch

videos.description: RB Squally Canada takes the hand-off and runs behind good blocking for a 9-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: BYU keeping foot on the gas with another TD

videos.description: On 4th & 5, the Cougars elect to go for it. Mangum throws a 41-yard pass to Micah Simon and he scores his second touchdown of the day.
videos.headline: BYU gambles and comes up with a TD

videos.description: Montel Aaron finds Tre Walker on a completion of 30-yards then Walker rolls over the defender for a touchdown.
videos.headline: San Jose scores its first TD of game
